This paper deals with reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence. The paper also discusses Markov decision processes, which are a type of stochastic process used in control theory and operations research. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
